</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/I5s6VHBHqig" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/27/apple-will-fix-iphone-13-unlock-with-apple-watch-soon/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=apple-will-fix-iphone-13-unlock-with-apple-watch-soon</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>【有片睇】iPhone 13 玻璃強度測試，外國 Drop Test 結果令人有驚喜</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/cpbwtH9uuxw/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Sun, 26 Sep 2021 08:31:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1062538</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>iPhone 13 推出後不少媒體都會進行不同性能、功能測試，而 YouTube 上有頻道就測試 iPhone [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>iPhone 13 推出後不少媒體都會進行不同性能、功能測試，而 YouTube 上有頻道就測試 iPhone 13 跌落地後的損壞情況，分別將 iPhone 13, iPhone 13 Pro Max 從桌面位置、一般人常講電話的位置，以及 2 米高度跌落石屎地面，看看 iPhone 全新玻璃的強度。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55-612x580.jpg" alt="" width="612" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55-612x580.jpg 612w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55-950x900.jpg 950w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55-768x727.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55-1536x1455.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.55.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 612px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-694x483.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="483" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-694x483.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-1280x890.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-768x534.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-1536x1068.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35-2048x1424.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.26.35.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>YouTube 頻道「EverythingApplePro」近日就發表了一段 iPhone 13 Pro「Drop Test」掉落測試影片。在測試影片中可看到就算是從桌面高度，或者測試者頭頂位置的高度掉下，即使是機面撞地還是機邊撞地，iPhone 13 Pro Max 前面與向面的玻璃仍然原好無缺，只是不鏽鋼邊緣有擦損痕跡，連測試者也表示驚奇；然而 iPhone 13 Pro 就沒有這樣好彩，雖然通過了桌面高度的落下測試，但在測試者頭頂高度的位置掉下石屎地面，就令到 iPhone 13 Pro 前面屏幕的玻璃爆裂。儘管如此，兩部 iPhone 仍然能夠運作良好。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-694x417.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="417" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-694x417.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-1280x769.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-768x462.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-1536x923.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-2048x1231.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.05-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-694x415.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="415" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-694x415.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-1280x765.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-768x459.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-1536x918.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-2048x1225.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.25.23-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-694x427.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="427" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-694x427.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-1280x788.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-768x473.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-1536x946.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36-2048x1261.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.28.36.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>之後在 10 尺高（約 3 米）位置再次進行測試，首先是以機身邊緣落地的掉下測試，這此測試中 iPhone 13 Pro 的背面玻璃也碎裂了，反而 iPhone 13 Pro Max 仍然只在不鏽鋼邊緣產生了一些擦損痕跡。而到了機身表面落地的測試，iPhone 13 Pro Max 始終還是爆裂了。測試者再嘗試於同一高度，以機背玻璃落地，玻璃同樣出現爆裂情況。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1062543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-2048x1153.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/螢幕截圖-2021-09-26-下午 4.24.48-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>最後測試者嘗試在加入保護殼的情況下，在 10 尺高地方進行掉落測試，發現主機毫無損傷，因此他建議使用者使用保護殼。</p><p>由於每次落地手機所承受的力度都有所不同，因此測試數據只能作參考。但也證明了就算在不高的位置跌落地，iPhone 13 Pro 還是有機會不爆玻璃，甚至原好無缺。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_51963"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332"  src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MxZhVAfJjmc?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="autoplay; encrypted-media" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MxZhVAfJjmc">YouTube</a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
